"Os yw'r fersiwn diweddaraf o Firefox gennych, yna mae Hello gennych eisoes."

#: firefox/hello.lang:42
msgid "There’s no account or sign-in required and nothing extra to download."
msgstr ""
"Does dim angen cyfrif na mewngofnodi a dim byd ychwanegol i'w lwytho i lawr."

#: firefox/hello.lang:46
msgid ""
"Just start a conversation, send your friend a link and ask them to click it."
msgstr ""
"Dim ond cychwyn sgwrs, anfon dolen at ffrind a gofyn iddyn nhw glicio arno."

#: firefox/hello.lang:50
msgid "Simple."
